---
// RitualSection.astro - Candle Care Guide
---

<section id="ritual" class="ritual">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="ritual__header">
      <span class="ritual__label">Experiencia</span>
      <h2 class="ritual__title">El Ritual de Cuidado</h2>
      <p class="ritual__description">
        Sigue estos pasos para prolongar la vida de tu vela y disfrutar de una fragancia óptima en cada encendido.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="ritual__grid">
      <div class="ritual__step">
        <div class="ritual__step-number">01</div>
        <div class="ritual__step-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="32" height="32" fill="none" class="icon-svg">
            <circle cx="6" cy="6" r="3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
            <circle cx="6" cy="18" r="3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
            <line x1="20" y1="4" x2="8.12" y2="15.88" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
            <line x1="14.47" y1="14.48" x2="20" y2="20" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
            <line x1="8.12" y1="8.12" x2="12" y2="12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="ritual__step-title">Recorte de Mecha</h3>
        <p class="ritual__step-content">
          Antes de cada encendido, recorta la mecha a unos 5mm. Esto evita el humo negro y asegura un quemado uniforme.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="ritual__step">
        <div class="ritual__step-number">02</div>
        <div class="ritual__step-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="32" height="32" fill="none" class="icon-svg">
            <path d="M12 2c0 0-3 2.5-3 6 0 1.5 1 3 3 3 2 0 3-1.5 3-3 0-3.5-3-6-3-6z" fill="currentColor" fill-opacity="0.2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
            <rect x="8" y="11" width="8" height="11" rx="1" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="ritual__step-title">El Primer Encendido</h3>
        <p class="ritual__step-content">
          Deja que la cera se derrita hasta los bordes del envase. Esto evita que se forme un "túnel" en el centro.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="ritual__step">
        <div class="ritual__step-number">03</div>
        <div class="ritual__step-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="32" height="32" fill="none" class="icon-svg">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
            <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="ritual__step-title">Tiempo Ideal</h3>
        <p class="ritual__step-content">
          No enciendas la vela por más de 4 horas seguidas. Deja que la cera se solidifique completamente antes de volver a usarla.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="ritual__step">
        <div class="ritual__step-number">04</div>
        <div class="ritual__step-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="32" height="32" fill="none" class="icon-svg">
            <path d="M5 9c0-1.8 1.5-3.3 3.3-3.3 1.8 0 3.3 1.5 3.3 3.3v7.3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
            <path d="M11 9c0-2.8 2.2-5 5-5s5 2.2 5 5v7.3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
            <path d="M2.5 19h19" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="ritual__step-title">Apagado Seguro</h3>
        <p class="ritual__step-content">
          Usa un apagavelas en lugar de soplar. Esto evita salpicaduras de cera y mantiene el aroma puro en el ambiente.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="ritual__tip">
      <div class="ritual__tip-content">
        <strong style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:0.5rem;">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
            <line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12" y2="12"/>
            <line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12.01" y2="8"/>
          </svg>
          Tip de Alquimista:
        </strong> Una vez terminada la vela, limpia el envase con agua tibia y jabón. ¡Son perfectos para decorar o guardar accesorios!
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .ritual {
    padding: var(--space-xl) 0;
    background: var(--color-bg);
  }

  .ritual__header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-xl);
  }

  .ritual__label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    background: rgba(212, 163, 115, 0.1);
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
  }

  .ritual__title {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .ritual__description {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
  }

  .ritual__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .ritual__step {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .ritual__step-number {
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: -10px;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 4rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .ritual__step-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .ritual__step-title {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .ritual__step-content {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .ritual__tip {
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
    padding: var(--space-md);
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent);
    border-radius: 0 var(--radius-md) var(--radius-md) 0;
  }

  .ritual__tip-content {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .ritual__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-md);
    }
  }
</style>
